    "name": "无心骇客：序章",
    "steam_appid": 3168820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/c3f27fcde3a13f012899c49cdae0adb6.poster.avif?t=1753077310\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/c3f27fcde3a13f012899c49cdae0adb6.webm?t=1753077310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/c3f27fcde3a13f012899c49cdae0adb6.mp4?t=1753077310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《Coreless》是一款第三人称、单人动作类 Roguelike 游戏，通过灵活的天赋与能力系统，为元进度玩法注入全新体验。玩家可从多种不同角色中选择，使用天赋点强化他们，并装备独特的插件（Addon）。每一次冒险都带来不同的挑战与独特体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/c4e77e6faabd9616472007b22db20f6f.poster.avif?t=1753077310\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/c4e77e6faabd9616472007b22db20f6f.webm?t=1753077310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/c4e77e6faabd9616472007b22db20f6f.mp4?t=1753077310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高度可自定义的角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过天赋、插件与战斗中的临时能力自由搭配，塑造你的战斗风格。你可以是远程输出的法术施放者、拥有眩晕与持续伤害能力的近战战士，或召唤小兵制造混乱的刺客。解锁新角色、能力与插件，打造独一无二的流派！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/10d70485d6e48ada1be08e1f7b5c4cd6.poster.avif?t=1753077310\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/10d70485d6e48ada1be08e1f7b5c4cd6.webm?t=1753077310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168820/extras/10d70485d6e48ada1be08e1f7b5c4cd6.mp4?t=1753077310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于 Tick 的插件系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险过程中，越能经受挑战，你就能获得更多 Tick——这代表你的表现。每达到一定 Tick 数值，你会获得插件掉落，并触发词缀里程碑以强化已有插件。插件是构建流派的核心：被动插件可能在开局赋予能力、周期性瘟疫敌人、或在敌人被瘟疫影响时为你提供护盾甚至额外生命。事件插件则根据所插入的插槽产生战斗优势——如双冲刺时收集增益，或触发超载技能后的连击效果。Tick 越多，掉落越强——生存越久，回报越大！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化且具有挑战性的遭遇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次游戏都充满了升级选择、多变的敌人，以及隐藏的解锁奖励。你需要在每个节点中尽可能成长，在“热度值”达 100% 前做好准备应对强大的 Boss。击败这些独特敌人可获取丰厚战利品，为后续冒险打下基础。更高难度、新地图与新敌人类型也将随之解锁，挑战与奖励并存。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不断成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使失败也不白费努力——你将获得永久提升，例如天赋点、插件和资源。这些成长将为下一次尝试带来更多策略空间与构筑选择。</p>",
